<body>
    <h2><center>CSS</center></h2>
    <p>
        Cascading Style Sheets, referred to as CSS, is a simple language intended 
        to simplify the process of making web pages presentable. 
        CSS allows you to apply style to web pages independent of the HTML 
        that makes up each web page.
    </p>
    <p>There are three ways of inserting a style sheet:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>External CSS</li>
        <li>Internal CSS</li>
        <li>Inline CSS</li>
    </ol>
    <p>CSS Selectors</p>
    <ol>
       <li>CSS element selector</li>
       <li>CSS id selector</li>
       <li>CSS class selector</li>
       <li>CSS universal selector</li>
    </ol>
